3. cs.SOC (Computational Social Science) - The paper deals with social networks and their properties, which is a key area of computational social science. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses graph extraction, visualization, and network statistics, which are all related to data structures and algorithms.
